{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Screening is a classification task, an area in which application of AI has strong potential.",
    "For example, apps that incorporate automatic speech recognition (ASR)",
    "and transcription have been used to detect mild cognitive impairment, an early indicator of Alzheimer's disease (Fristed et al., 2022).",
    "Similarly, ASR tools have assisted in screening children for speech sound disorders (Suthar et al., 2022).",
    "Another promising approach pairs physical objects with an interactive app to distinguish children with developmental language disorders from typically developing peers (Beccaluva et al., 2024)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "and transcription have been used to detect mild cognitive impairment, an early indicator of Alzheimer's disease (Fristed et al., 2022).",
